-- Four Former OPEC Ministers Establish Energy Consulting Group
-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 2012-03-12T12:49:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-12/four-former-opec-ministers-establish-energy-consulting-group.html
Former oil ministers from OPEC
nations  Algeria ,  Iraq ,  Libya  and  Nigeria  established a group to
offer advice on  energy policy  and business strategy.  Chakib Khelil from Algeria, Issam Chalabi from Iraq, Shokri
Ghanem from Libya and Rilwanu Lukman from Nigeria said in an e-
mailed statement that the association will be based in Vienna.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
 gsmith52@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  